'''Ecosia'''是一个总部位于[[德国|德国]][[柏林|柏林]]的[[搜索引擎|搜索引擎]]，他們将100%的利润捐赠给[[非營利組織|非營利組織]]，用于种植树木。<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title=What is Ecosia?|url=https://ecosia.org/what|accessdate=2015-01-20|publisher=Ecosia|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190113021751/https://www.ecosia.org/what}}</ref>Ecosia是{{Tsl|en|B Lab}}认证的公益企业。他們宣称實踐了碳吸收<ref name="TC">{{cite web|title=How does Ecosia neutralize a search's CO2 emissions?|url=https://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201531072-How-does-Ecosia-neutralize-a-search-s-CO2-emissions-|accessdate=2019-03-03|work=Zendesk|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328125253/https://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201531072-How-does-Ecosia-neutralize-a-search-s-CO2-emissions-|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使用[[再生能源|再生能源]]为[[伺服器|伺服器]]供能，保持財務透明，还保护用户的隐私。<ref name="Register">{{cite news|last1=Oates|first1=John|title=Green search engine Ecosia thinks Google's Android auction stinks, gives bid a hard pass|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/08/12/green_search_engine_rejects_googles_android_auction_offer/|accessdate=2019-09-05|work=The Register|publisher=Situation Publishing|date=2019-08-12|language=en|archive-date=2019-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915021819/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/08/12/green_search_engine_rejects_googles_android_auction_offer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://docs.google.com/a/ecosia.org/document/d/13-p39IfNkxi71ercV3sb7f81HsFQf31EZsllezcy60s/edit?usp=sharing |title=Donation Statements, Ecosia |publisher=Google, Ecosia |accessdate=2015-01-20 |archive-date=2016-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409045823/https://docs.google.com/a/ecosia.org/document/d/13-p39IfNkxi71ercV3sb7f81HsFQf31EZsllezcy60s/edit?usp=sharing |dead-url=no }}</ref>Ecosia还获得了B Lab的认证。截止2020年7月，Ecosia种植的树木总数已超过1亿株，每月从大气中吸收超过5万吨的[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]。该搜索引擎被[[Google_Chrome|Chrome]]和[[Firefox|Firefox]]纳入默认搜索引擎选项<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=德國環保搜尋引擎 廣告收入全球種樹|url=https://news.pts.org.tw/article/509296|accessdate=2021-01-19|author=施慧中|date=2021-01-18|publisher=公視新聞|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304041831/https://news.pts.org.tw/article/509296}}</ref>，而在[[iOS|iOS]] 14.3、[[iPadOS|iPadOS]] 14.3中也被加入到[[Safari|Safari]]的搜尋引擎選項中。

== 搜索引擎 ==
Ecosia最初提供了[[雅虎|雅虎]]的搜索结果与[[Bing|必应]]、[[维基百科|维基百科]]的技术组合。广告由雅虎提供，作为与雅虎收入分享协议的一部分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alternative Suchmaschinen - "Googeln" für den Regenwald|url=https://www.sueddeutsche.de/digital/alternative-suchmaschinen-googeln-fuer-den-regenwald-statt-fuer-google-1.2116129|accessdate=2020-08-05|last=Zeitung|first=Süddeutsche|work=Süddeutsche.de|language=de|archive-date=2020-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628052159/https://www.sueddeutsche.de/digital/alternative-suchmaschinen-googeln-fuer-den-regenwald-statt-fuer-google-1.2116129|dead-url=no}}</ref>

现在，Ecosia的搜索结果由必应提供，并由公司自己的算法增强。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Where do Ecosia's search results come from?|url=http://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/206153381|accessdate=2020-08-05|work=Ecosia's FAQ|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105231059/https://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/206153381|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Ecosia致力于保护用户隐私。搜索会被加密，不会永久存储，Ecosia也不会将数据出售给第三方广告商。Ecosia在隐私政策中声明，它不创建基于搜索历史记录的个人配置文件，也不使用任何诸如[[Google分析|Google分析]]的外部跟踪工具。<ref>{{Cite web|title=We protect your privacy|url=https://info.ecosia.org/privacy?ref=fb-share|accessdate=2020-08-06|author=|date=|format=|work=info.ecosia.org|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015202212/https://info.ecosia.org/privacy?ref=fb-share|dead-url=no}}</ref>

<!-- Ecosia的服务器使用可再生能源供能，并宣布实现了碳吸收。但最初不适用于Microsoft或Yahoo!使用的搜索技术。但现在微软的部分服务器也开始使用可再生能源。<ref>{{Internetquelle |url=https://www.microsoft.com/about/csr/environment/renewable_energy/ |titel=Renewable Energy {{!}} Microsoft Environment |sprache=en-US |abruf=2017-01-24}}</ref> -->
Ecosia宣称，在该网站每次搜索会获得0.005[[欧元|欧元]]的广告收益，而种植一棵树的成本为0.25欧元，因此每搜索50次所获得的广告收益足够种一棵树{{NoteTag|但是Ecosia首页显示的是45次。}}。这些树木在15年的预计寿命内，平均每棵能吸收50千克[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]。如果Ecosia的市场占有率达到现在[[Google搜索|Google]]的水平，他们所种的树木能吸收全球二氧化碳总排放量的15%，足以抵消全球汽车[[尾气|尾气]]排放。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How does Ecosia neutralize a search's CO2 emissions?|url=http://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201531072|accessdate=2020-08-06|work=Ecosia's FAQ|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021144947/https://ecosia.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201531072}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:Re_publica_19_-_Day_3_(46886393095)_(cropped).jpg|缩略图]]Ecosia于2009年12月7日启动，恰逢[[联合国|联合国]]在[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]举行的气候谈判。<ref name="TWE">{{cite web|title=Microsoft-Backed Green Search Engine Attacks Google|url=http://www.techweekeurope.co.uk/e-innovation/microsoft-backed-green-search-engine-attacks-google-2661|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2009-12-04|last=Donoghue|first=Andrew|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723125050/http://www.techweekeurope.co.uk/e-innovation/microsoft-backed-green-search-engine-attacks-google-2661|archive-date=2015-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>随着时间的推移，Ecosia支持了各种植树项目。2010年12月之前，Ecosia的资金都捐赠给了[[世界自然基金会|世界自然基金会]]德国分会的一个项目，用于保护[[亚马逊盆地|亚马逊盆地]]的朱鲁埃纳国家公园。

2011年，Ecosia的筹款超过25万欧元。<ref>{{cite web|title=Green search engine means you click and save the rainforest|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/damian-carrington-blog/2011/jun/03/green-economy-searchengines|date=2011-06-03|last=Carrington|first=Damian|website=The Guardian|access-date=2018-11-20|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222161203/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/damian-carrington-blog/2011/jun/03/green-economy-searchengines|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从2013年7月到2014年9月，Ecosia支持了[[大自然保护协会|大自然保护协会]]运营的“种植10亿棵树”（Plant a Billion Trees）<ref>{{cite web|title=Plant a Billion Trees|url=https://documents.ecosia.org/467540/12104650|website=Plant a Billion Trees|access-date=2018-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407185038/https://documents.ecosia.org/467540/12104650|archive-date=2019-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>项目。该项目旨在于2015年前种植100万棵本土树木，以恢复巴西大西洋森林。

2015年，在[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]和[[世界银行|世界银行]]的支持下，Ecosia开始为[[布基纳法索|布基纳法索]]的植树造林项目捐赠，这是旨在防止[[荒漠化|荒漠化]]的[[非洲绿色长城|非洲绿色长城]]项目的一部分。

Ecosia是B-labs认证的公益企业。B-labs称，截止2015年1月，“搜索引擎自2009年12月成立以来，将80%的广告收入捐出，筹资超过150万美元用于保护雨林”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ecosia GmbH, B Corporation|url=http://www.bcorporation.net/community/ecosia-gmbh|accessdate=2015-01-20|publisher=B-labs|archive-date=2015-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120184737/http://www.bcorporation.net/community/ecosia-gmbh|dead-url=yes}}</ref>截止2015年，Ecosia有近250万活跃用户，种植的树超过200万棵。

2015年5月，Ecosia被评选为“欧洲科技初创企业奖”的“欧洲之星”，入围“旨在改善社会的最佳欧洲初创企业”。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Shortlist Is Out – Vote Now In The Europas Awards For European Tech Startups|url=https://techcrunch.com/2015/05/18/vote-now-in-the-europas-awards-for-european-tech-startups/|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-05-18|last=Butcher|first=Mike|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230134920/https://techcrunch.com/2015/05/18/vote-now-in-the-europas-awards-for-european-tech-startups/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年10月9日，Ecosia试图以100万欧元的价格从能源公司[[莱茵集团|莱茵集团]]手中收购Hambach森林，以阻止该森林因褐煤开采而被砍伐，<ref>{{cite web|title=Berlin startup offers €1m to save ancient Hambach forest from coal mining|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/oct/09/berlin-startup-offers-1m-to-save-ancient-hambach-forest-from-coal-mining|date=2018-10-09|last=Connolly|first=Kate|website=the Guardian|access-date=2018-11-20|archive-date=2019-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113184358/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/oct/09/berlin-startup-offers-1m-to-save-ancient-hambach-forest-from-coal-mining|dead-url=no}}</ref>但被莱茵集团拒绝。 <ref>{{cite web|title=Berlin startup offers €1m to save ancient Hambach forest from coal mining|url=https://www.leonardodicaprio.org/tree-planting-search-engine-ecosia-offers-to-buy-germanys-hambach-forest-to-save-it-from-destruction/|date=2018-10-25|last=Kroll|first=Christian|website=The Leonardo DiCaprio Foundation|access-date=2020-07-14|archive-date=2018-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012054740/https://www.leonardodicaprio.org/tree-planting-search-engine-ecosia-offers-to-buy-germanys-hambach-forest-to-save-it-from-destruction/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从2020年1月23日起，Ecosia将其获得的利润捐赠给了[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]ReForest Now。该组织不仅计划恢复森林，而且宣称能使该地区更能抵御未来的火灾。ReForest Now宣称将使用这些钱种植26446棵树。<ref>{{Cite web|title=On Thursday, all searches will plant trees in Australia|url=https://blog.ecosia.org/trees-for-australia/|date=2020-01-20|last=Joshi|first=|website=Ecosia Blog|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128072425/https://blog.ecosia.org/trees-for-australia/|archive-date=2020-01-28|access-date=2020-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia searches will plant 26,446 trees in Australia!|url=https://blog.ecosia.org/ecosia4aus/|date=2020-01-24|last=Joshi|first=|website=Ecosia Blog|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200205133240/https://blog.ecosia.org/ecosia4aus/|archive-date=2020-02-05|access-date=2020-01-24}}</ref>

2020年10月，Ecosia宣布购买了[[银行卡|银行卡]]公司[[TreeCard|TreeCard]]20％的股份<ref name=":3">{{cite web|title=TreeCard - The wooden debit card that plants trees|url=https://www.treecard.org/|publisher=TreeCard|language=en|access-date=2020-10-15|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605090427/https://www.treecard.org/}}</ref><ref name="Neowin-Treecard">{{cite web|title=Ecosia will fund tree-planting with spend on wooden debit card.|url=https://www.neowin.net/news/ecosia-will-fund-tree-planting-with-spend-on-wooden-debit-card|author=Paul Hill|date=15 October 2020|publisher=Neowin|language=en|access-date=2020-10-15|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318012922/https://www.neowin.net/news/ecosia-will-fund-tree-planting-with-spend-on-wooden-debit-card/}}</ref>，并计划在2021年与[[万事达|万事达]]合作推出新的[[银行卡|银行卡]]。<ref name="Business-Insider-TreeCard">{{cite web|title=Here's an exclusive look at the pitch deck a 23-year-old Y Combinator alum used to raise $1 million for ethical bank cards.|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/treecard-eco-fintech-launches-with-1m-seed-funding-from-ecosia-2020-10?international=true&r=US&IR=T|author=Callum Borroughs|date=15 October 2020|publisher=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|language=en|access-date=15 October 2020|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408055349/https://www.businessinsider.com/treecard-eco-fintech-launches-with-1m-seed-funding-from-ecosia-2020-10?international=true&r=US&IR=T}}</ref>在这项计划中，TreeCard将使用英国[[樱桃木|樱桃木]]制成的木质卡（每棵树可制成30万张木质卡），以取代普通的[[塑料|塑料]]银行卡<ref name="Neowin-Treecard" /><ref name="Business-Insider-TreeCard" />，并将80％的利润用于Ecosia的植树项目。根据计算，客户需要花费60美元来资助一棵树。<ref name="Neowin-Treecard" />银行卡还可以链接到[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]、[[Google_Pay|Google Pay]]和[[Samsung_Pay|Samsung Pay]]完成支付。目前TreeCard已经开放注册。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia投资TreeCard 木质借记卡的经营收入将资助植树活动|url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1041075.htm|accessdate=2021-02-20|date=2020-10-15|last=cnBeta|publisher=cnBeta|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019083024/https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1041075.htm}}</ref><ref name=":3" /><ref name="Neowin-Treecard" />

