== 影响 ==
[[File:Ecosia_Trees_Map.svg|缩略图]]
根据Ecosia的博客，目前Ecosia的项目覆盖27个国家或地区，包括[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]、[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]、[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]、[[海地|海地]]、[[巴西|巴西]]、[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]、[[塞内加尔|塞内加尔]]、[[布吉納法索|布基纳法索]]、[[加纳|加纳]]、[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]、[[乌干达|乌干达]]、[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]、[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]]、[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]、[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]、[[苏丹|苏丹]]、[[马里|马里]]、[[英国|英国]]、[[科特迪瓦|科特迪瓦]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[卢旺达|卢旺达]]、[[玻利维亚|玻利维亚]]、[[美国|美国]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[印度|印度]]和[[马拉维|马拉维]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Where Ecosia plants trees {{!}} Projects by country|url=https://blog.ecosia.org/tag/where-does-ecosia-plant-trees/|accessdate=2021-02-20|publisher=Ecosia Blog|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415165157/https://blog.ecosia.org/tag/where-does-ecosia-plant-trees/}}</ref>

截止2020年7月，Ecosia种植的树木总数超过了1亿株，每月从大气中吸收超过5万吨的二氧化碳。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia users have planted 100 million trees: a milestone and a beginning!|url=https://blog.ecosia.org/100-million/|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2020-07-09|work=The Ecosia Blog|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809111333/https://blog.ecosia.org/100-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Europe's green search engine Ecosia reaches milestone of 100 million trees planted|url=https://www.eu-startups.com/2020/07/green-search-engine-ecosia-reaches-100-million-trees-planted-milestone-in-fight-against-climate-crisis/|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2020-07-09|last=Ohr|first=Thomas|work=EU-Startups|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817123613/https://www.eu-startups.com/2020/07/green-search-engine-ecosia-reaches-100-million-trees-planted-milestone-in-fight-against-climate-crisis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Ecosia search engine approaches 100 million planted trees|url=https://www.neowin.net/news/ecosia-search-engine-approaches-100-million-planted-trees|accessdate=2020-08-05|last=Neowin ·|first=Paul Hill|work=Neowin|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725013521/https://www.neowin.net/news/ecosia-search-engine-approaches-100-million-planted-trees|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Want to feel benefits of a break? Don't give up the day job ...|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/10/want-feel-benefits-break-dont-give-up-the-day-job|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2020-07-10|accessdate=2020-08-05|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Mark|last=Rice-Oxley|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804010524/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/10/want-feel-benefits-break-dont-give-up-the-day-job|dead-url=no}}</ref>同月报道，通过广告收益，Ecosia平均每0.8秒就能种一棵树，每分钟种75棵，每天种108,000棵。<ref name=":1" />

== 浏览器集成和应用程序 ==
Ecosia的扩展程序可分别从[[Chrome网上应用店|Chrome网上应用商店]]或[[Mozilla|Mozilla]]的[[附加组件_(Mozilla)|Add-ons]]下载。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia - The search engine that plants trees|url=https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ecosia-the-search-engine/eedlgdlajadkbbjoobobefphmfkcchfk|accessdate=2020-08-17|publisher=Google网上应用店|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817133213/https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ecosia-the-search-engine/eedlgdlajadkbbjoobobefphmfkcchfk}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia — The search engine that plants trees 🌱 – 下载 🦊 Firefox 扩展|url=https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-CN/firefox/addon/ecosia-the-green-search/|accessdate=2020-08-05|author=Ecosia Dev Team|date=|format=|publisher=Firefox Add-ones|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626210247/https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-CN/firefox/addon/ecosia-the-green-search/}}</ref>

在2018年3月，Firefox在59.0版本中将Ecosia添加到德语版的搜索引擎选项中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Firefox 59.0, See All New Features, Updates and Fixes|url=https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/59.0/releasenotes/|accessdate=2021-03-27|date=2018-03-13|publisher=Mozilla|language=en|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909035148/https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/59.0/releasenotes/}}</ref>

从2020年3月12日起，Ecosia被列为Google Chrome的默认搜索引擎选项，成为首个被列入的非盈利搜索引擎。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tree planting search engine Ecosia is getting a visibility boost in Chrome|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2020/03/12/tree-planting-search-engine-ecosia-is-getting-a-visibility-boost-in-chrome/|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=Natasha Lomas|date=2020-03-12|publisher=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref>

2020年12月14日，[[苹果公司|苹果]]的Safari网络浏览器在MacOS Big Sur 11.1、iOS 14.3和iPadOS 14.3中也将Ecosia列为默认搜索引擎选项。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia now a default search engine option on iOS, iPadOS, macOS|url=https://appleinsider.com/articles/20/12/14/ecosia-now-a-default-search-engine-option-on-ios-ipados-macos|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=Wesley Hilliard|date=2020-12-14|publisher=AppleInsider|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518004135/https://appleinsider.com/articles/20/12/14/ecosia-now-a-default-search-engine-option-on-ios-ipados-macos}}</ref>

2021年1月28日，Ecosia宣布与[[Brave浏览器|Brave浏览器]]建立合作关系，被纳入Brave浏览器的官方搜索引擎之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Introducing a better internet: Ecosia is now available on Brave, the privacy browser|url=https://blog.ecosia.org/brave/|accessdate=2021-03-27|date=2021-01-28|publisher=The Ecosia Blog|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225210615/https://blog.ecosia.org/brave/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ecosia is now an Official Search Engine Option on Brave|url=https://brave.com/ecosia/|accessdate=2021-03-27|date=2021-01-28|last=Brave|publisher=Brave Browser|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224010305/https://brave.com/ecosia/}}</ref>

Ecosia还发布了基于[[Chromium|Chromium]]的[[免费软件|免费]][[网页浏览器|网页浏览器]]EcoBrowser，可用于[[Android|Android]]、[[iOS|iOS]]、[[Windows|Windows]]、[[MacOS|MacOS]]。<ref name=":0" />

